titles.title: An original resolution to authorize expenditures of the Committee on the Judiciary.

calendar.text: Committee on Judiciary ordered to be reported an original measure.

action.text: Committee on Judiciary. Original measure reported to Senate by Senator Biden. Without written report.
Referred to the Committee on Rules.

calendar.text: Committee on Rules. Provisions of measure incorporated into measure S.RES. 71 ordered to be reported.

bill.summary: 2/4/1993--Introduced. Authorizes expenditures by the Senate Committee on the Judiciary for the 103d Congress.
